    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
      Loafers Guide
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600">
      Everything you need to know about loafers: from the classic penny loafer to horsebit designs. Learn about the history, styling, and construction of these versatile slip-on shoes.
